1
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:27,920
Let me introduce myself.

2
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,440
I am

3
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,050
Heavenly Official,

4
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,840
Lu Sinian.

5
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,440
Greetings, miss.

6
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,250
My name is Yuyao.

7
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:40,250
I'm in charge of tending to Yaochi.

8
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,289
Nice to meet you,

9
00:01:41,320 --> 00:01:41,979
Miss Yuyao.

10
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,570
I look forward to

11
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:44,759
working with you.

12
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,290
Are you okay?

13
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:25,840
I'm fine.

14
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,460
The Jiao snake's magic is getting stronger.

15
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,880
We need to reinforce the Sea-Calming Needle.

16
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:40,540
From now on,

17
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,880
don't act alone anymore.

18
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,120
Yuyao.

19
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:58,840
Yuyao.

20
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:42,690
Come.

21
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,320
Under the divine official's care,

22
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,440
the fairy gradually recovered her vitality.

23
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:51,520
She discovered that beneath the divine official's cold exterior

24
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:52,680
lay a warm heart.

25
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,840
His love for this land...

26
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,290
And his protectiveness

27
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,640
made her admire him.

28
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,160
As time passed by,

29
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:01,640
their feelings

30
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,840
were like the water in Jade Pool,

31
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:04,960
clear

32
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,200
and pure.

33
00:07:28,400 --> 00:07:28,800
Yuyao.

34
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,520
This is the hairpin

35
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,050
I brought back from Heaven.

36
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,180
Let me put it on for you.

37
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,490
It looks beautiful.

38
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,020
From now on,

39
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,120
it's yours.

40
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,520
From now on...

41
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,320
Big guy,

42
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:05,400
are you leaving?

43
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:06,800
But the water monster in Jade Pool

44
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,880
hasn't been completely eliminated yet.

45
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,280
Yuyao.

46
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,200
I have something to tell you.

47
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,180
I also have something to tell you.

48
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,170
Then let me go first.

49
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,850
Mine is more important.

50
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,400
I'll go first.

51
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,520
This ring

52
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:33,039
was forged by me

53
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:34,890
using a lot of magic.

54
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,440
Lu Sinian, let me ask you.

55
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,650
Are you willing to be with me

56
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,220
and be my lover?

57
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,360
I promise,

58
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,400
I will treat you well.

59
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,320
You just need to watch the house. I'll support you.

60
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,650
No matter what happens,

61
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,450
I will always stay by your side.

62
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,540
I will never leave you.

63
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,970
Are you willing?

64
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:04,440
They witnessed the changing of the seasons at Yaochi together,

65
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,840
and experienced the snow, rain, wind, and frost together.

66
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,120
Their love story

67
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:11,000
became a legend passed down by people.

68
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,840
Is the place where they were together

69
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,440
located at

70
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,080
Bogda Peak?

71
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,850
The story in the dream should be like this.

72
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:28,640
What Xuan Qing said

73
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:30,300
about the story of my past life

74
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,560
might be true.

75
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:37,720
What's wrong?

76
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,600
Do you have a headache again?

77
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,660
It's because you skipped breakfast.

78
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:45,440
I have some cookies here. Do you want some?

79
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,080
I'm fine.

80
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,540
I just find it strange.

81
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,330
These are obviously

82
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,080
stories from legends.

83
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:53,660
Why do I feel

84
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:55,520
so familiar

85
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,120
with all of this?

86
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:59,360
It'd be weird if you weren't.

87
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:09,920
Then,

88
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,970
what happened next?

89
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,480
Later,

90
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,740
what happened to them?

91
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:18,840
It's a pity.

92
00:11:20,760 --> 00:11:22,290
The good times didn't last.

93
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:33,480
Yuyao,

94
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:35,880
I'm going back to the Heavenly Court.

95
00:11:35,880 --> 00:11:37,200
I'll bring you a gift when I return.

96
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:37,730
Alright.

97
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,130
What do you want?

98
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,920
I want to eat pastries made by the Queen Mother.

99
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,040
If you sweet-talk her,

100
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:46,920
it will work much better than if I do.
